OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774865180
OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio has
OL,7,Fsaid the conflict in the Middle East
OL,8,Fwill end in "weeks not months" after a
OL,9,Fdifficult meeting with his G7
OL,10,Fcounterparts on Friday.
OL,12,FIt comes as Iran's state media says
OL,13,Fits nuclear facilities were hit, just
OL,14,Fhours after Israel threatened to
OL,15,F"escalate and expand" its campaign
OL,16,Fagainst Tehran.
OL,18,FSpeaking to reporters after the
OL,19,Fmeeting in France concluded, Rubio
OL,20,Fsaid: "We are very confident we are on
OL,21,Fthe verge of achieving them very soon."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774865180
OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FWhen asked how long until the conflict
OL,7,Fended, Rubio said: "We are talking
OL,8,Fweeks, not months."
OL,10,FHe also said the US can achieve its
OL,11,Fmilitary aims "without any ground
OL,12,Ftroops", amid speculation the US was
OL,13,Fconsidering putting boots on the
OL,14,Fground in Iran, with thousands of
OL,15,FAmerican marines moved to the area.
OL,17,FOn Thursday, US President Donald Trump
OL,18,Fextended his pause on striking Iranian
OL,19,Fenergy facilities by 10 days, saying
OL,20,Fnegotiations with Tehran were going
OL,21,Fwell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774865180
OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FThe Iranian government has repeatedly
OL,7,Fdenied that it was in discussion with
OL,8,FWashington.
OL,10,FAt the G7 meeting, Rubio cut a lone
OL,11,Ffigure, with the other six member
OL,12,Fnations all reluctant to get involved
OL,13,Fin the conflict.
OL,15,FTrump's repeated criticisms of Nato
OL,16,Fand European nations for their lack of
OL,17,Fenthusiasm over the conflict did not
OL,18,Fimprove the mood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774865180
OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FTrump has repeatedly complained that
OL,7,Fallies have ignored or rejected
OL,8,Frequests for help confronting Tehran's
OL,9,Fretaliation, including the closure of
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz to most
OL,11,Finternational shipping.
OL,13,FOn Thursday, he said: "We are very
OL,14,Fdisappointed with Nato because Nato
OL,15,Fhas done absolutely nothing."
OL,17,FHe also criticised the UK's response
OL,18,Fto the conflict and compared the UK's
OL,19,Faircraft carriers to "toys."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
