OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FAhead of the meeting, the French
OL,7,Fforeign minister said the war "is not
OL,8,Fours", while British Foreign Secretary
OL,9,FYvette Cooper diplomatically said the
OL,10,FUK supported "defensive action" while
OL,11,Ftaking a "different approach" to
OL,12,F"offensive action."
OL,14,FThe diplomats at the meeting also
OL,15,Fdiscussed reopening the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz, with the Iranian blockade
OL,17,Fputting an increased strain on the
OL,18,Fglobal economy as well as pressure on
OL,19,FWashington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
