OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FThree ships of different nationalities
OL,7,Fwere not allowed to pass through the
OL,8,Fstrait on Friday, Iran's Revolutionary
OL,9,FGuards said on its Sepah News website.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
