CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774865180
OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FThe United States has offered Iran a
OL,7,F15-point proposal for a ceasefire that
OL,8,Fincludes it relinquishing control of
OL,9,Fthe strait, but at the same time has
OL,10,Fordered thousands more troops to the
OL,11,Fregion, possibly in preparation for a
OL,12,Fmilitary attempt to wrest the waterway
OL,13,Ffrom Iran.
OL,15,FIran maintains it is not engaged in
OL,16,Fany negotiations.
OL,18,FIn Iran, IRNA state media claimed a
OL,19,Fheavy-water plant and a yellowcake
OL,20,Fproduction plant were struck.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
