PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774865180
OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FYellowcake is a concentrated form of
OL,7,Furanium after impurities are removed
OL,8,Ffrom the raw ore. Heavy water is used
OL,9,Fas a moderator in nuclear reactors.
OL,11,FThe strikes did not cause any
OL,12,Fcasualties, and there was no risk of
OL,13,Fcontamination, it said.
OL,15,FIt came hours after Israel vowed to
OL,16,Fexpand its campaign.
OL,18,FDefence Minister Israel Katz said Iran
OL,19,F"will pay heavy, increasing prices"
OL,20,Ffor retaliatory strikes on Israel.
