OL,3,CIran war to end in 'weeks not months'
OL,4,CRubio says as strikes continue
OL,6,FThe Israeli military issued an "urgent
OL,7,Fwarning" to Iranians in the central
OL,8,Fcity of Arak on Friday afternoon,
OL,9,Fstating that they should immediately
OL,10,Fleave for their "safety and well-
OL,11,Fbeing".
OL,13,FIran also continues to attack American
OL,14,Fallies in the region, with Iranian
OL,15,Fmissiles damaging two ports in Kuwait
OL,16,Fon Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
